docs.lead_paragraph: Widespread interest has been awakened here in a meeting tomorrow of Rotary members of Argentina, Chile, Uruguay and Paraguay on the frontier of Chile and Argentina at the foot of the gigantic statue of Christ, which, with arms extended toward the territories of the two countries, symbolizes the ties of friendship between them.
